24:22.927 --> 24:24.463
Where is everything?

24:24.563 --> 24:28.200
What happened to the cells?
What's going on?

24:28.300 --> 24:29.985
What...? What's going on?

24:30.335 --> 24:32.572
Where is everything?

24:33.338 --> 24:36.555
I want you to think
of the Anne Frank house.

24:37.742 --> 24:40.004
Oh, yeah. Anne Frank!

24:40.478 --> 24:42.680
Fucking brilliant.

24:45.516 --> 24:46.785
You're a genius.

24:46.885 --> 24:49.388
- Come again.
- You're a fucking genius.

24:49.488 --> 24:52.996
- Where's the door?
- You ask and you shall receive.

24:54.793 --> 24:57.210
We did do a door, right?

25:00.765 --> 25:02.368
Good job.

25:02.468 --> 25:07.840
"Respond to our ransom demand
by the deadline

25:07.940 --> 25:11.409
"by running the code word 'Notice'

25:11.509 --> 25:16.462
"in the newspaper or you'll never see
Heineken or Doderer ever again."

25:19.184 --> 25:21.002
Okay.

25:21.152 --> 25:22.586
Take it.

25:38.602 --> 25:41.070
Can you fucking stop that?

25:50.347 --> 25:51.464
Okay, it's time.

26:35.926 --> 26:38.630
- Shit.
- No, it's nothing.

26:38.730 --> 26:42.601
- You don't know that.
- Look, it's nothing. It's just a coincidence.

26:42.701 --> 26:45.404
There's always an excuse
if you're looking for it.

26:45.504 --> 26:48.887
If we're going to do this, we do it now.

26:56.280 --> 26:57.296
Here we go.

27:01.752 --> 27:04.456
Alright, let's go.

27:04.556 --> 27:06.172
Let's go.

27:13.297 --> 27:17.817
Now remember, if we need to speak,
then we only speak in German.

27:37.789 --> 27:39.824
We'll be in touch.

27:43.761 --> 27:45.321
Alright.

27:50.529 --> 27:52.151
What's going on? What are you doing?

27:56.174 --> 27:57.817
Who are you?

27:59.911 --> 28:03.462
Let me go! Let me go!

28:10.321 --> 28:12.872
Dumb shit! Get into the fucking van!

28:26.904 --> 28:28.020
What?

29:53.190 --> 29:55.377
Alright, alright, alright.

30:09.441 --> 30:11.093
Okay.

30:14.579 --> 30:16.618
Alright, okay, okay, okay.

30:18.916 --> 30:21.286
Alright, let me have all their clothes.

30:21.386 --> 30:24.212
- Come on.
- That's nice. I'll get the barrel.

30:26.623 --> 30:29.828
- Hey, can we talk now?
- Yeah, we can talk. I told you to speak in German!

30:29.928 --> 30:32.745
- Your man didn't fight like mine.
- Enough!

30:40.738 --> 30:42.824
Alright, listen.

30:43.074 --> 30:49.030
Listen. Did anybody leave
their fingerprints on this ransom note?

30:49.914 --> 30:56.330
I'll ask again. Did anybody
touch this with their bare hands?

30:56.430 --> 30:58.172
- I may have.
- Oh, fuck.

30:59.391 --> 31:01.927
Alright. Is there anybody next door?

31:02.027 --> 31:04.829
- They should have left by now.
- Come with me. Come on.

31:04.929 --> 31:08.314
- Let's start.
- Willem, where do I start?

31:36.093 --> 31:37.986
The copier is there.

31:54.578 --> 31:57.235
Let's go. Let's go, let's go.

31:59.149 --> 32:01.208
It's okay. We got a new one.

32:03.854 --> 32:05.871
You got his watch?

32:14.498 --> 32:17.168
Alright. Now remember,

32:17.268 --> 32:20.571
once you're done with that,
you make out like it's any other night.

32:20.671 --> 32:22.981
- All right, we'll be at the bar.
- I'll be there.

32:23.081 --> 32:26.978
It's our alibi. Hey, kid. You good?

32:27.078 --> 32:29.962
Yeah? You sure? Alright, good.

32:35.619 --> 32:39.808
Just don't think about it
being a police station, alright?

32:40.158 --> 32:43.762
Ever think you'd deliver
an invoice for 35 million?

32:43.862 --> 32:47.772
- Are they really going to pay all that?
- They have to.

32:51.602 --> 32:53.865
Can't we just mail it?

32:54.539 --> 32:56.188
Come on.

32:58.041 --> 32:59.878
Take your breath.

32:59.978 --> 33:02.079
Breathe. Go.

33:20.432 --> 33:23.458
It's not exactly my favorite
neighborhood either.

33:39.149 --> 33:40.886
- Package is delivered, boys.
- You good?

33:40.986 --> 33:42.413
We're heading home.

33:42.513 --> 33:46.075
Cat, Cat, Cat. Stay for one minute.
Come on, stay for one.

33:47.125 --> 33:49.143
Yeah, one drink, one drink.

33:49.668 --> 33:51.836
You alright?

33:52.764 --> 33:54.716
Do it.

33:55.066 --> 33:56.601
Ring the bell!

33:56.701 --> 33:58.284
Ring it!

34:19.156 --> 34:22.393
- You guys do it up right last night?
- Well, you know me.

34:22.493 --> 34:24.862
We made sure we were seen
and we kept it respectable.

34:24.963 --> 34:26.664
- Good.
- You?

34:26.764 --> 34:30.163
Oh, it was riveting. I fell asleep
watching cartoons with the kids.

34:31.869 --> 34:33.440
Yeah.

34:40.409 --> 34:42.679
Well? How are they?

34:42.780 --> 34:45.295
Heineken's fine. Pissed off.

34:47.551 --> 34:49.868
The driver is not too good.

35:19.784 --> 35:21.959
Now you listen to me.

35:22.387 --> 35:25.640
You are in no danger here.

35:25.990 --> 35:30.000
As long as the money is paid,
you will be released. Do you understand?

35:35.832 --> 35:37.672
Hey, guys.

35:39.303 --> 35:40.954
Check it out.

36:20.144 --> 36:22.286
Do you have a name?

36:22.880 --> 36:24.120
No name.

36:24.615 --> 36:27.462
Is it ransom or money?

36:30.220 --> 36:31.883
Are you the boss?

36:33.057 --> 36:35.059
Okay, you're the boss.

36:35.159 --> 36:38.074
So, I have a few requests.

36:38.463 --> 36:42.500
I'd like a bathrobe, slippers,

36:42.600 --> 36:46.353
a shaving kit, comb, mirror,

36:47.637 --> 36:49.824
reading glasses,

36:50.897 --> 36:52.706
a decent fucking chair...

36:53.711 --> 36:59.064
and what else? Oh, yes, and if it's not
too much trouble, a telephone.

37:01.752 --> 37:04.006
You have no name?

37:05.022 --> 37:07.802
You're part of an organization?

37:08.326 --> 37:11.579
You're Baader Meinhof? Red Brigade?

37:11.729 --> 37:15.258
IRA? Symbionese Army?

37:20.737 --> 37:22.040
- Hey, Cor.
- What?

37:22.140 --> 37:24.675
- Look at this.
- What?

37:24.775 --> 37:26.244
- Oh, fuck.
- You're going to love it.

37:26.344 --> 37:29.147
Nice. Nice, nice.

37:29.247 --> 37:31.015
Says five guys involved.
How many have you?

37:31.115 --> 37:34.195
- This one says three.
- Yeah, listen to this. Listen.

37:34.419 --> 37:39.624
"An unknown number of most certainly
dangerous and experienced criminals."

37:39.724 --> 37:42.156
- Let me see, let me see.
- It's perfect.

37:42.256 --> 37:44.483
More about this morning's top story...

37:44.630 --> 37:47.332
Alfred Heineken,
the billionaire of brewing magnate,

37:47.432 --> 37:50.268
was kidnapped by a group of heavily
armed men yesterday...

37:50.368 --> 37:53.872
- I know who did it.
- Corporate in Amsterdam.

37:53.972 --> 37:55.940
Police have now confirmed that they...

37:56.040 --> 37:58.893
- Who?
- Bud.

37:59.443 --> 38:00.912
Weiser. Bud Weiser.

38:01.012 --> 38:04.025
Yeah? One way to beat the competition?

38:05.249 --> 38:07.614
Funny guy?

38:08.053 --> 38:11.489
Police would not disclose
the size of the ransom demanded

38:11.589 --> 38:13.972
but it is assumed to be significant.

38:16.026 --> 38:17.328
What?

38:17.428 --> 38:18.897
- The ransom note.
- What?

38:18.997 --> 38:20.398
- The ransom note.
- What do you mean?

38:20.498 --> 38:23.117
- Did we leave it? In the copier?
- No, no.

38:23.667 --> 38:27.071
...until he was threatened
by the kidnappers with a machine gun.

38:27.171 --> 38:30.604
Wait, did we...? No, did we?

38:33.009 --> 38:35.463
Oh, fuck.

38:54.766 --> 38:56.334
Hey...

38:56.434 --> 38:58.136
- George.
- George, yeah.

38:58.236 --> 38:59.437
- Remember me?
- Yeah.

38:59.537 --> 39:01.773
- How's it going?
- Same old, same old.

39:01.873 --> 39:04.275
- So everything's alright?
- I guess.

39:04.375 --> 39:06.790
Do you mind if we make a quick copy?
Me and the guys.

39:06.890 --> 39:08.346
- Go ahead.
- Thank you.

39:08.446 --> 39:10.119
Thank you.

39:42.145 --> 39:43.890
Thank you.

39:50.754 --> 39:52.590
Thank you for that, too.

39:52.690 --> 39:56.733
I assume you...
sent a note about the ransom.

39:56.833 --> 39:59.046
Did they reply?

39:59.296 --> 40:01.275
Well, they will.

40:05.970 --> 40:08.215
In the meantime, this music,

40:08.315 --> 40:12.417
it's beautiful and laden
with tragic disillusion, but...

40:12.767 --> 40:15.379
the same tape
over and over again, all day long,

40:15.479 --> 40:19.301
please, I know I am your prisoner but
there's no need to torture me, my friend.

40:20.251 --> 40:24.956
Some Johann Sebastian Bach
would be quite soothing. Or, well...

40:25.056 --> 40:29.560
Franz Fucking Schubert, anything.
Silence, preferably.

40:29.660 --> 40:31.996
Also, some books would pass the time

40:32.096 --> 40:35.350
and as much as I adore
ham sandwiches, my friend,

40:36.000 --> 40:38.846
Chinese food is quite easy to get,

40:38.946 --> 40:43.274
and it's cheap too, and... I know,
something like, let me think...

40:43.374 --> 40:45.493
yeah, Bang Bang chicken.

40:45.843 --> 40:49.161
With some extra chili sauce,
how about that? Okay?

40:55.185 --> 40:57.284
Happy birthday. Cheers.

40:58.790 --> 41:02.009
You'll be looking for
a regular paycheck now, hey.

41:02.624 --> 41:05.046
Finally. I can serve the cake now.

41:05.196 --> 41:06.981
Hi, honey.

41:07.131 --> 41:09.517
No more fooling around?

41:09.634 --> 41:12.270
- My son Mark, he drives a tram.
- Yeah, I know Mark.

41:12.370 --> 41:15.952
Yeah, he's got good hours.
Most importantly, he's got a good pension.

41:17.375 --> 41:20.432
- You'd have to take the training first.
- Really? They train?

41:20.532 --> 41:23.428
- I could have a word with him...
- Could you?

41:25.216 --> 41:28.088
Always the same stupid joke.

41:29.821 --> 41:32.223
From my daughter as well, now?
Wonderful.

41:32.323 --> 41:34.291
What a kind and thoughtful gift,
thank you.

41:34.391 --> 41:36.998
Pa, it was a joke.

41:37.995 --> 41:40.999
Cannot you at least wait
till they let Mr. Heineken go?

41:41.099 --> 41:43.471
- If they ever do let him go.
- Don't start on this again.

41:43.571 --> 41:47.606
If I get those filthy bastards,
I will kill them. Kill them!

41:47.839 --> 41:51.556
Willem, please, it's Pa's birthday.
Come on.

41:58.114 --> 42:02.273
Cat? How long do you reckon it'll take
Heineken's people to pay the ransom?

42:03.247 --> 42:04.773
Cat?

42:05.122 --> 42:08.574
- How long do you reckon it'll...?
- No more questions.

42:09.126 --> 42:11.110
Because I don't have the answers.

42:19.470 --> 42:22.240
Thanks.
Hey, and thanks for the new music.

42:22.340 --> 42:24.743
It's very whimsical, very droll.

42:24.843 --> 42:27.361
Yeah. Got books! Good.

42:27.611 --> 42:28.905
Alright.

42:29.880 --> 42:31.328
Any luck with the Bang Bang?

42:34.185 --> 42:35.757
No?

42:42.259 --> 42:44.779
Some guys like Bang Bang chili
all the time.

42:45.129 --> 42:48.299
But you like sweet sour.
Ever since five years.

42:48.399 --> 42:52.837
Sweet sour pork, sweet sour prawn,
sweet sour beef. You're a sweet sour guy.

42:52.937 --> 42:55.844
So it's Chinese, right?
Now me is a chili guy.

42:55.994 --> 42:59.825
Okay, okay. You a goddamn Bang Bang man.

43:03.447 --> 43:05.416
- Right.
- See you tomorrow.

43:05.516 --> 43:07.165
What can I get for you?

43:08.820 --> 43:10.417
Wake up.

43:10.667 --> 43:12.578
Fuck you, man.

43:14.825 --> 43:17.294
- Did they run the notice?
- Not yet.

43:17.394 --> 43:20.398
Come on, man, this was only
supposed to take five days.

43:20.498 --> 43:23.101
What if he is sick?
We gotta kidnap a fucking doctor?

43:23.201 --> 43:25.887
- Is he sick?
- No.

43:26.337 --> 43:29.922
Don't get too personal.
Or he'll get inside your head.

43:41.251 --> 43:45.222
Look, leather jacket, Popeye. Cops?

44:01.504 --> 44:06.009
Willem, even if they are cops,
it doesn't mean anything.

44:06.109 --> 44:09.046
- You okay?
- Fuck, I'm just done waiting.

44:09.146 --> 44:11.630
Yeah, I know. I know. Alright? Me, too.

44:22.960 --> 44:24.397
What are you trying to do?

44:30.367 --> 44:31.979
Yeah.

44:33.571 --> 44:37.474
If you tell the Police where I am,
I could give you half the ransom and...

44:37.574 --> 44:39.059
a house in Switzerland.

44:39.309 --> 44:43.214
Lots of beautiful Swiss girls,
blond, they're beautiful.

44:43.314 --> 44:45.279
I'll...

44:46.317 --> 44:49.025
I'll arrange it as many as you like.

44:49.920 --> 44:52.323
No? You're not interested?

44:52.423 --> 44:55.025
Are you gay or something?

44:55.125 --> 44:57.724
Any news from the Police?

45:09.539 --> 45:12.113
- It's been over two weeks now.
- The longer they don't pay the money,

45:12.213 --> 45:14.826
the more time they have
to figure out who did it.

45:16.679 --> 45:18.473
You want to give up?

45:19.216 --> 45:20.887
I do.

45:21.285 --> 45:23.237
You what?

45:23.387 --> 45:24.928
I do, yeah.

45:26.056 --> 45:28.059
Let's let him go.

45:28.659 --> 45:32.847
Knock down the cells, burn everything.

45:34.022 --> 45:36.317
Okay, we don't get the money,

45:36.867 --> 45:38.969
but you know what we do get?

45:39.069 --> 45:41.455
- Our lives back.
- Oh, come on.

45:41.805 --> 45:45.827
Come on, look, they're just messing
with us. That's all that is.

45:46.577 --> 45:49.346
Cat, where you going? Really? Cat...

45:49.446 --> 45:51.715
- Wait!
- We failed!

45:51.815 --> 45:54.578
It's my fucking shed. I want him
out of there. Before it's too late.

45:54.678 --> 45:58.489
Look, just listen! Just listen.
Listen, listen, alright?

45:58.589 --> 46:00.408
Look, it's all just part of the game.

46:01.158 --> 46:03.127
We're still in control here.

46:03.227 --> 46:07.827
You really want to walk out
on 35 million?

46:09.566 --> 46:12.841
What we got to do
is make the transaction.

46:13.370 --> 46:15.384
Thirty-five million.

46:20.243 --> 46:23.971
- Someone has got to relieve Brakes.
- Alright.

46:25.182 --> 46:27.131
I'm going home.

46:59.482 --> 47:01.609
They didn't pay.

47:02.052 --> 47:04.469
You've got to be kidding me.

47:04.922 --> 47:07.370
What do you mean they didn't pay?

47:07.958 --> 47:09.758
Last night was the deadline.

47:10.628 --> 47:14.598
We told them that we would kill you
if they didn't pay.

47:14.698 --> 47:16.467
And they didn't fucking pay!

47:16.567 --> 47:19.453
- So time's up!
- Okay.

47:19.803 --> 47:21.726
There must be some confusion.

47:23.440 --> 47:25.442
It's confusion, that's it.

47:27.511 --> 47:30.581
Damn, I'm their boss! Nobody else.

47:30.681 --> 47:33.784
Must be out of their fucking minds.
I'll fire them all!

47:33.884 --> 47:36.804
Give me a pen and paper.
Give me a pen and paper now!

47:36.954 --> 47:40.274
And you're all fired! You as well.
Don't worry, you'll get your blood money.

47:40.524 --> 47:43.819
You know you will. You have
my word of honor. Okay? Okay?!

47:44.361 --> 47:48.716
You fucking morons! Yeah.
What's his problem?

47:49.066 --> 47:51.185
- What?
- Now you listen to me.

47:51.735 --> 47:54.084
Can we also have your...

47:56.073 --> 48:00.945
Can we also have your word of honor
right now, in writing,

48:01.045 --> 48:05.015
that when you're free,
you won't help the police in any way?

48:05.115 --> 48:07.435
- My word of honor?
- Yeah.

48:07.885 --> 48:11.840
Yeah. That's the way the game is played.

48:13.123 --> 48:14.898
You've got my word.

48:15.693 --> 48:17.409
It's time to end it now, okay?

48:47.990 --> 48:49.574
Hello?

48:52.462 --> 48:54.798
Why is the door open? Hello?

48:54.898 --> 48:56.693
Ab, is that you?

48:58.936 --> 48:59.919
- Boss?
- Yeah.

49:00.019 --> 49:02.372
- Boss, are you alright?
- Yeah, I'm sort of okay.

49:02.472 --> 49:04.608
Tired of this crap.

49:04.708 --> 49:06.506
Oh, God.

49:07.244 --> 49:10.447
Are you okay? Have they left you alone
or given you a rough time?

49:10.547 --> 49:14.585
I don't know, I... I... I...
How long have we been in here now?

49:14.685 --> 49:18.656
A month? I don't know, I've lost track.
I'm a little confused, it feels longer.

49:18.756 --> 49:20.641
Now, now, I'll tell you now.

49:21.625 --> 49:22.819
It comes to...

49:24.528 --> 49:27.165
Almost three weeks.

49:27.463 --> 49:29.082
Yeah.

49:29.900 --> 49:34.234
Why the hell are you here?
You've got no money to offer these jokers.

49:34.334 --> 49:35.806
Well, if...

49:35.906 --> 49:38.876
If your people don't pay,

49:38.976 --> 49:44.548
then... then these guys need to prove
that they're not fooling around and...

49:44.648 --> 49:49.730
Well, it can't be your head...
they'll send to the police in a box.

49:50.788 --> 49:53.876
Don't worry, Ab.
We'll... pay whatever it takes.

49:53.976 --> 49:56.327
If it's a hundred million, we'll pay.

49:56.427 --> 49:59.046
I want to get out of this
as much as you guys.

49:59.296 --> 50:02.700
Alright? But we have to let them
sweat it out another week.

50:02.800 --> 50:06.203
Let them believe that
their screw-up killed Heineken.

50:06.303 --> 50:09.423
You remind me again
why we grabbed the driver.

50:10.073 --> 50:14.570
- Why? What's your point?
- A question the police are asking.

50:14.670 --> 50:17.848
Is... are these guys the real deal?

50:17.948 --> 50:21.130
Or are they just a bunch of pussies?

50:21.518 --> 50:25.405
And if the answer is
that they're a bunch of pussies,

50:27.424 --> 50:30.845
- they're going to string this out forever.
- So what are you trying to say?

50:31.995 --> 50:35.065
Well, we said if they don't pay,
then there'll be blood.

50:35.165 --> 50:37.601
You wrote that in the letter.

50:39.469 --> 50:40.696
This is business.

50:42.272 --> 50:44.594
It's nothing personal.

50:45.375 --> 50:47.384
And they didn't fucking pay.

50:51.849 --> 50:54.698
- I agree.
- Oh, really?

50:56.185 --> 50:58.121
- Yeah.
- Yeah?

50:58.221 --> 50:59.523
- Yeah? You agree?
- Yeah.

50:59.623 --> 51:02.659
With him? Alright, good. Big man,

51:02.759 --> 51:05.531
alright then, slice his fucking throat.

51:23.746 --> 51:25.539
I'll do it.

51:38.527 --> 51:39.723
Willem...

51:40.705 --> 51:42.499
Hey. Hey. Hey.

51:42.599 --> 51:45.586
- You're acting like a scared little boy.
- Hey, you fucking do it!

51:45.936 --> 51:48.527
A scared little boy.

51:51.064 --> 51:53.644
Fuck! I didn't sign up for this!

51:53.744 --> 51:57.548
Cor, if he does anything... anything!

51:57.648 --> 52:01.368
If he does anything in there,
it's fucking on you.

52:01.518 --> 52:04.812
- Do something!
- Fuck.

52:11.461 --> 52:12.829
Use your head!

52:12.929 --> 52:14.824
Oh, fuck.

52:21.838 --> 52:23.624
Oh, fuck.

53:10.119 --> 53:12.121
You alright?

53:12.722 --> 53:15.859
Stop what you're doing.
What are you doing?

53:15.959 --> 53:18.125
What are you doing?

53:18.762 --> 53:23.147
What are you doing?
Come here. Come on. Come on.

53:39.048 --> 53:42.248
- Is he alright?
- Yeah, no, he's okay. He's fine.

53:43.487 --> 53:44.991
We all just need to go home,

53:45.856 --> 53:50.093
take a breather, get drunk,
get laid, whatever you got to do.

53:50.193 --> 53:54.080
But we just got to stick to the routine
and we'll see each other in a few days.

53:55.098 --> 53:57.971
Alright. Let's go.

54:10.112 --> 54:12.981
In a case that has riveted
the nation and much of Europe,

54:13.081 --> 54:17.921
the kidnapping of billionaire
Alfred Heineken has entered its 19th day.

54:18.021 --> 54:20.457
With no substantial leads
and no end in sight,

54:20.557 --> 54:24.442
a massive manhunt involving local
and federal law enforcement continues.

54:32.502 --> 54:35.175
Oh, hey. Where've you been?

54:36.473 --> 54:40.944
- You were supposed to be at birth class.
- What? No, s... Fuck.

54:41.044 --> 54:43.029
No, no, no.

54:43.279 --> 54:46.583
Sonja! Listen, I'm sorry.
Listen, I'll make it up to you!

54:46.683 --> 54:50.202
