Sonja...

55:04.466 --> 55:07.618
Have they paid? Am I to be set free?

55:29.692 --> 55:32.325
Did you give them my message?

55:32.496 --> 55:36.750
You know, they have one more chance.

55:37.000 --> 55:39.386
If they screw it up this time...

55:39.536 --> 55:43.090
And they know I've given you my word
so they will pay, so...

55:43.840 --> 55:46.493
How are you planning to set us free?

55:46.643 --> 55:48.597
I will put...

55:48.697 --> 55:52.582
