56:33.356 --> 56:35.947
So congratulations, well done, and...

56:37.427 --> 56:40.989
soon you'll get your money
and then you will be...

56:41.539 --> 56:44.766
very, very rich.

56:45.435 --> 56:47.020
But...

56:47.970 --> 56:49.706
But what?

56:49.806 --> 56:53.525
No, what I meant to say,
my friend, is that...

56:53.810 --> 56:58.695
There are two ways a man can be rich
in this world. He can have a lot of money

56:59.249 --> 57:02.440
or he can have a lot of friends.

57:03.019 --> 57:05.474
But he cannot have both.

57:26.341 --> 57:28.289
Cor?

57:29.512 --> 57:30.947
Yeah?

57:31.047 --> 57:33.252
