to the shed and we'll let Heineken go.

01:03:14.991 --> 01:03:16.275
- And I like it!
- Let's do it!

01:03:16.375 --> 01:03:20.563
Police say the ransom was larger
than any paid in modern times.

01:03:20.663 --> 01:03:24.351
